== Ubuzima Bwite ==
Karen bugingo yavukiye i kigali ababyeyi be bapfuye muri Genocide yakorewe abatutsi, amashuri abanza yayize muri La Colombiere ayisumbuye ayarangiriza muri Lycee de [[kigali]], kaminuza ayiga Mount [[kenya]] aho yize ibyerekeye itangazamakuru.<ref>https://umutihealth.com/karen-bugingo-wakize-kanseri/</ref>

== Ibyerekeye igitabo cye ==
